Sheet1.Title: The Parallel World: Poetic film
Sheet1.Description:
The Parallel World is a video series depicting how much we are distracted from the real world when we remain in our comfort zones.

The distractions are huge. But not huge enough to grab my attention. Not big enough to sway my mind. The noise is unheard, so are the screams. Because here, in my space; in his, her and your space, all you hear and feel is the wind chiming and the ecstasy of being safe.

Sheet1.Title: The Grandmother
Sheet1.Description: It's a short Animated Film about the relationship between a boy and his Grandmother.
